@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.exp(0.66) * ((tmp + 0.80 / v0 + 0.88) - (v1 + 0.73 - v2 + 0.75)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.cos(0.38))
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.sin(wp.abs(v0 + 0.68)))
    v1 = wp.sin((wp.abs(v0 + 0.24) / (v1 + 0.46 / v0 + 0.20)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.exp(v2 + 0.67)) - wp.abs((v1 + 0.52 + v0 + 0.23)))
    tmp = (0.81 / 0.23)
    data[tid] = v0
